    <item>
      <title>Tech Tuesday Training: Working Together in Microsoft 365</title>
      <description><![CDATA[<div>  <img src="https://localist-images.azureedge.net/photos/52488156022240/huge/2d8cca0cf860768829e5b99179faa9f41cb3879b.jpg" style="width: 100%;" />  <div style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #555;"><strong>Tue, 05 May 2026</strong></div>  <div><p>Working Together in Microsoft 365: Collaboration, Sharing, and Permissions</p>

<p>This one‑hour workshop helps participants understand how sharing and permissions work in Microsoft 365, including SharePoint, OneDrive, and Teams. Every day, people share files without realizing who can see, edit, or reshare their content. This session explains those basics in a practical, easy‑to‑follow way. For more information, visit ETS Training</p>

